	<h1>Help</h1>
	<br/>
	<br/>
	<h2>Welcome to Memorize!</h2>
	<br/>
	<br/>
	<h3>How to play?</h3>

	<p>This app is a memory game where the goal is to match pairs. Touch on a card to discover what is underneath.</p>
	<p>There are 3 types of games:</p>
	<ul>
    		<li>Arithmetic</li>
    		<li>Images and Sounds</li>
    		<li>Letters</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Just load your favourite one and work on your memory to solve it!</p>

	<h3>New Game</h3>
	<p><img src="file:///android_res/drawable/restart.png" alt="new_game" width="70" height="70"><br/><br/>
	Click on this icon if you want to reload the game or start a new one. This action will change the order of the cards on the grid.</p>
	
	<h3>Change the size</h3>
	<p><img src="file:///android_res/drawable/size4.png" alt="change_size" width="70" height="70"> 
	You can choose the size of the grid:</p>
 	<ul>
    		<li>4 x 5</li>
    		<li>5 x 6</li>
    		<li>6 x 7</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Sometimes the game might not fill the screen because it has less pairs than the number you've selected.</p>	
	
	<h3>Load a specific game</h3>
	<p><img src="file:///android_res/drawable/addition.png" alt="specific_game_additions" width="70" height="70">
	<img src="file:///android_res/drawable/sounds.png" alt="specific_game_sounds" width="70" height="70">
	<img src="file:///android_res/drawable/letters.png" alt="specific_game_letters" width="70" height="70"></p>
	<p>You can load one of the demo games:</p>
	<ul>
    		<li><b>additions</b> : try to match the operation with the solution.</li>
    		<li><b>sounds</b>: attempt to recognize which instrument is playing and but also match with the good picture.</li>
    		<li><b>letters</b> : seek for the capital letter which match the small one.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>You can also load the games you create yourself with the <b>Editor</b>.</p>
	
	<h3>Change the theme</h3>
	<p><img src="file:///android_res/drawable/theme.png" alt="change_theme" width="70" height="70"><br/><br/>
	Choose your favourite theme for the patterns on the backs of the cards.</p>
	
	<h3>Editor</h3>
	<p><img src="file:///android_res/drawable/settings.png" alt="editor" width="70" height="70"></br>
	Create and edit your own memory game!<br/>
 	Enter a name longer than 3 characters, choose a type and add pairs to build your game!</p>

 	<table>
 	<ul>
	<li><b>Arithmetic:</b></br>
	Enter 2 numbers and select the operation (+ / - / *). <br/>
		When you are happy with your new pair, click on <img src="file:///android_res/drawable/pair_add.png" alt="add_pair" width="40" height="40"></li></br></br>
    	<li><b>Images and Sounds :</b></br>
	Choose an image from the gallery or take a photo with the camera. Choose a sound from the SD card or the media system.<br/>
	The supported formats are jpg/png for the pictures and mp3/ogg for the sounds.<br/>
	When the paths are corrects, this icon will appear : <img src="file:///android_res/drawable/import_ok.png" alt="import_ok" width="20" height="20"><br/>
	If you see this icon : <img src="file:///android_res/drawable/import_cancel.png" alt="import_cancel" width="20" height="20">, it means there was a problem to find one of the files. Please choose amn other one.</li></br></br>
    	<li><b>Letters :</b></br>
	Enter a letter and the matched card will be this same text in capital letter.</li></br></br>
	<p>If you want to delete a specific pair, click on : <img src="file:///android_res/drawable/delete_pair.png" alt="delete_pair" width="20" height="20"><br/>
	If you want to delete all the pairs shown on the gallery, click on : <img src="file:///android_res/drawable/edit_clear.png" alt="delete_gallery" width="30" height="30"></p>
	<p>When you are happy with all the pairs you have created, save your game and you will be able to play it. You just have to click on this icon : <img src="file:///android_res/drawable/save.png" alt="save_game" width="40" height="40"> and follow the instructions.</p>
	<p>Note: you need to create at least 10 pairs to have a usable game</p>
